reviewText: I love watching the old Betty Boop cartoons. This was a good selection of them.

Betty Boop 6  This collection  is what children should be watching today- not that violent  stuff on TV today.  Very bad manners and languuage is what TV  is all about today.  This is what I was brought up with-Betty Boop,Bugs Bunny,Wood Woodpecker and so on-good laughs
